cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.DS 

This paper is about improving the convergence of adaptive gradient methods (AGMs) in deep learning, which is a topic closely related to machine learning (cs.LG), neural networks (cs.NE), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also provides theoretical analysis and empirical studies, which involve optimization algorithms and data analysis, respectively, indicating that it may also belong to the data structures (cs.DS) category.
